item.content:encoded:
Diksha IIT Academy is an Institute providing training to the students aspiring for IIT / VIT / NIT / BIT SAT / State Board since 2008. We have also started Foundation Program for Class 6th, 7th, 8th, 9th& 10thstudents from 2012. Details of our program are given below.

1.Our Programs:

  • Coaching for State Board syllabus.
  • Coaching for CBSE syllabus.
  • Foundation for IIT & Medical.
  • Debate on science curriculums.
  • Competitive training (Work Shop).

2. Our Batches :

  • 6th, 7th, 8th, 9th& 10th(Junior Section) :Includes : Board, CBSE, NTSE, MTSE, Science Olympaid, IIT/Med Foundation etc.
  • 11th& 12th(Senior Section) :Includes : Board, IIT-JEE, NIT, VIT-EEE, BITSAT.

3. Our Target :

  • To achieve progress before one year in the concerned class.
  • To nurture competitive environment for students.

4. Teaching Methodology :

Level 1

Based on Single concept.

Level 2

Based on dual concept.

Level 3

Based on multiple concept.

Level 4

Brain teasers.

5. Our macro & micro analysis for students :

Tests Pattern :

Subjective pattern, objective pattern.

Type of Tests

Class Test, Weekly Test, Unit Test, Middle session test, Test Series Full Test, Scholarship Test.

6. Self study program under guidance :

  • 2 to 4 Hrs Every Day
  • Practice Session
  • Doubt Clearing Session

7. Our scholarship Program :

  • Admission CUM Scholarship Program - Aptitude Test CUM Scholarship Program

8. Free Tuition Fee Program for :

  • Top Rankers in admission cum scholarship test.
  • Talented students with poor financial status.

9. Full time library facility :

  • With a wide range of books by reputed authors and publication.

10. Hostel facility :

  • An affordable hostel facility is provided by the academy for the students.

item.content:encoded:
A shared vision of excellence in the ignited minds of experienced faculty member led to DIKSHA IIT ACADEMY came into existence on 20th January 2008. Driven by a shared pursuit of results, the founders of DIKSHA IIT ACADEMY are determined to be the trend setters in the field of JEE (Main + Advanced), VITEEE, BIT SAT preparation.

Faculty at DIKSHA IIT ACADEMY are from reputed institutes of Delhi & Kota and they are highly experienced in teaching methodology, optimizing time, maximizing performance which is followed by the reputed institutes of Delhi & Kota, which led to more than thousand selection in JEE (Main+Advanced) every year

At the outset, we would like to emphasize that DIKSHA IIT ACADEMY is committed towards the goal of JEE (Main+Advanced). For our students , we are the dues - ex - machina of JEE Main+Advanced. Commitment has a new face at DIKSHA IIT ACADEMY, we demand unwavering resilience from our students and reward intelligence in ample measure.

At DIKSHA IIT ACADEMY Success becomes habit not just in exams - But in life as well. A competitive environment, cutting edge knowledge pool, scientifically developed teaching methodology put us far ahead of our competitors . Highly experienced, dedicated and highly trained faculty ensure that students obtain that critical edge which gives students a clear lead in the pursuit of their goal.
